Package: OncoRegimenTester
Title: Synthetic OMOP CDM Simulator for Oncology Regimen Detection Testing
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "author@example.com")
Description: White-box simulator that generates fake but structurally believable
    oncology treatment histories in OMOP-like tables. Designed for method testing,
    algorithm development, and benchmarking regimen detection logic using
    interpretable CSV parameter packs. Supports CDMConnector CDM reference
    objects for direct integration with OHDSI tooling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
